(156, 1, '2022-05-04 03:43:16', '2022-05-04 00:43:16', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":31,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"about-img\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full about-img\"><img src=\"http://localhost/profserdar/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/hakkimda.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-31\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Resume</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A professor who accepts patients in the medical unit of Neurosurgery of the Brain and Nervous System (Neurosurgery). Dr. Serdar Albayrak completed his medical Dec at Marmara University Faculty of Medicine between 1991 and 1998. between 1998 and 2004, he completed his Decisional education at the Department of Neurosurgery of Istanbul University Istanbul Faculty of Medicine and earned the title of Neurosurgery Specialist (Neurosurgery).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>His research interests include treatment applications related to many diseases, especially epilepsy and brain tumors, as well as innovative applications such as brain battery surgeries (Parkinson\'s dystonia Decaying disease), tumor surgery, pain treatment, micro surgery, Gamma Knife. He also specializes in such areas as epilepsy surgery, microsurgical treatment of brain tumors, treatment of cerebral vascular tangles and bubbles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Prof. Dr. Serdar Baki Albayrak yurtdışında ABD’de Harvard Üniversitesi Hastanesi’nde ve Finlandiya’da Helsinki Üniversitesi Hastanesi’nde ameliyat ve araştırma doktoru olarak çalışmıştır.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The physician who applies surgical treatments using the most advanced methods provided by medical technology has received high-level education abroad in the USA and Germany regarding many of the procedures he has performed. In the medical field as well as our country\'s education Albayrak, many successfully completed education and work internationally, and has earned various certifications in different countries in the world having experience in 48 patients. In addition to tumor surgery, he has also conducted cancer research and has learned about innovative treatments in the field of biotechnology.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"about-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns about-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Okullar/Eğitimler</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>İstanbul Marmara Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi – Tıp Fakültesi (Lisans), 1991 – 1998</li><li>İstanbul Üniversitesi İstanbul Tıp Fakültesi – Uzmanlık eğitimi (Beyin cerrahisi ihtisası), 1998 – 2004</li><li>Harvard Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi – 1 Yıl Klinik Fellow-Burslu, 2007 – 2008</li><li>Helsinki Üniversitesi – 1 Yıl Klinik Fellowship, 2006 – 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Deneyimler</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Helsinki Üniversitesi Toolo Hospital, Klinik Fellowship – Beyin anevrizmaları (baloncukları), AVM leri (beyin damar anomalileri) ve kompleks beyin tümörlerinin tedavisi konusunda ihtisas sonrası eğitim aldım ve ameliyatlara katıldım.</li><li>Harvard Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi Brigham and Women Hospital, Klinik Fellow-burslu – Beyin tümörlerinin tedavisi konusunda bu programda ameliyat doktoru olarak da görev alan beyin cerrahisi uzmanı oldum.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"about-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns about-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Ödüller</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Harvard Üniversitesi, Boston- ABD, Beyin Tümörleri, 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Bilinen Diller</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>İngilizce</li><li>Türkçe (Anadil)</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Prof. Dr. Serdar Baki Albayrak', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-05-04 03:43:16', '2022-05-04 00:43:16', '', 16, 'http://localhost/profserdar/?p=156', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(89, 1, '2022-04-27 05:40:01', '2022-04-27 02:40:01', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":31,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"about-img\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full about-img\"><img src=\"http://localhost/profserdar/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/hakkimda.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-31\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Özgeçmiş</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Beyin ve Sinir Cerrahisi (Nöroşirürji) tıbbi biriminde hasta kabul eden Prof. Dr. Serdar Albayrak, 1991-1998 yılları arasında Marmara Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi’nde tıp lisansını tamamlamıştır. 1998-2004 yılları arasında İstanbul Üniversitesi İstanbul Tıp Fakültesi Nöroşirürji Anabilim dalında uzmanlık eğitimini tamamlayarak Beyin ve Sinir Cerrahisi (Nöroşirürji) uzmanı unvanını kazanmıştır.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>İlgi alanları arasında başta epilepsi ve beyin tümörü gibi birçok hastalığa ilişkin tedavi uygulamaları ile beyin pili ameliyatları (Parkinson distoni titreme hastalığı), tümör cerrahisi, ağrı tedavisi, mikro cerrahi, Gamma Knife gibi yenilikçi uygulamalar yer almaktadır. Epilepsi cerrahisi, beyin tümörlerinin mikrocerrahi tedavisi, beyin damar yumakları ve baloncuklarının tedavisi gibi alanlarda da uzmanlaşmıştır.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Prof. Dr. Serdar Baki Albayrak yurtdışında ABD’de Harvard Üniversitesi Hastanesi’nde ve Finlandiya’da Helsinki Üniversitesi Hastanesi’nde ameliyat ve araştırma doktoru olarak çalışmıştır.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tıp teknolojisinin sağlamış olduğu en gelişmiş yöntemleri kullanarak cerrahi tedaviler uygulayan hekim, uyguladığı işlemlerin birçoğuna ilişkin üst düzey eğitimlerini yurtdışında ABD ve Almanya’da almıştır. Tıp alanında ülkemizde almış olduğu eğitimlerin yanı sıra Albayrak, uluslararası anlamda birçok eğitim ve çalışmayı başarıyla tamamlamış, dünyanın 48 değişik ülkesinde hasta tedavi tecrübesi edinmiş ve çeşitli sertifikasyonları almaya hak kazanmıştır. Tümör cerrahisinin yanı sıra kanser araştırmaları da yapmış, biyoteknoloji alanında yenilikçi tedaviler hakkında bilgi edinmiştir.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"about-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns about-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Okullar/Eğitimler</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>İstanbul Marmara Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi – Tıp Fakültesi (Lisans), 1991 – 1998</li><li>İstanbul Üniversitesi İstanbul Tıp Fakültesi – Uzmanlık eğitimi (Beyin cerrahisi ihtisası), 1998 – 2004</li><li>Harvard Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi – 1 Yıl Klinik Fellow-Burslu, 2007 – 2008</li><li>Helsinki Üniversitesi – 1 Yıl Klinik Fellowship, 2006 – 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Deneyimler</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Helsinki Üniversitesi Toolo Hospital, Klinik Fellowship – Beyin anevrizmaları (baloncukları), AVM leri (beyin damar anomalileri) ve kompleks beyin tümörlerinin tedavisi konusunda ihtisas sonrası eğitim aldım ve ameliyatlara katıldım.</li><li>Harvard Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi Brigham and Women Hospital, Klinik Fellow-burslu – Beyin tümörlerinin tedavisi konusunda bu programda ameliyat doktoru olarak da görev alan beyin cerrahisi uzmanı oldum.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"about-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns about-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Ödüller</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Harvard Üniversitesi, Boston- ABD, Beyin Tümörleri, 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Bilinen Diller</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>İngilizce</li><li>Türkçe (Anadil)</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Prof. Dr. Serdar Baki Albayrak', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-04-27 05:40:01', '2022-04-27 02:40:01', '', 16, 'http://localhost/profserdar/?p=89', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(190, 1, '2022-05-16 03:40:16', '2022-05-16 00:40:16', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":31,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"about-img\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full about-img\"><img src=\"http://localhost/profserdar/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/hakkimda.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-31\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Resume</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Dr. Albayrak is a dedicated academic, innovator and practising neurosurgeon who accepts and treat patients worldwide from over fifty countries so far. Hundreds of international patients were treated by his expertise in Istanbul, Turkey.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>After having completed medical school and neurosurgery training in Istanbul, He did subspeciality trainings (clinical fellowships) in the top medical centers of the world- Brain tumor surgery at B&amp;W Hospital at Harvard Medical School, Boston, United States and the cerebrovascular surgery at Helsinki University Toolo Hospital, Finland.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Along with thousands of general neurosurgical cases he operated, his main interest areas include the micro-neurosurgical management of complex brain and skull base tumors, brain aneurysms, arteriovenous malformations, cavernomas, epilepsy, functional neurosurgery, and spina bifida/spasticity surgeries.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>He has numerous international publications in respected journals with hundreds of citations.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Prof. Albayrak has several ongoing research projects regarding the treatment of gliomas-one of the challenging brain tumors to treat- and for restoration of neuronal transmission in spinal cord injury.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Dr. Albayrak is a founding member of medical innovation group, Innoway RG and he has currently over 25 patent applications with eight granted patents.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"about-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns about-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Schools/Trainings</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Istanbul Marmara University Faculty of Medicine – Faculty of Medicine (Bachelor\'s Degree), 1991 – 1998</li><li>Istanbul University Istanbul Faculty of Medicine - Specialty training –Specialization in neurosurgery), 1998 – 2004</li><li>Harvard University School of Medicine - 1 Year Clinical Fellow-Scholarship Holder, 2007 – 2008</li><li>University of Helsinki - 1 Year Clinical Fellowship, 2006 – 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Experiences</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>İstanbul Marmara Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi - Tıp Fakültesi (Lisans), 1991 - 1998</li><li>İstanbul Üniversitesi İstanbul Tıp Fakültesi - Uzmanlık eğitimi -Nöroşirürji Uzmanlığı), 1998 - 2004</li><li>Harvard Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi - 1 Yıllık Klinik Burs Sahibi, 2007-2008</li><li>Helsinki Üniversitesi - 1 Yıllık Klinik Burs, 2006 - 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"about-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns about-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Awards</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Harvard University, Boston- USA, Brain Tumors, 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Known Languages</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>English</li><li>Türkçe (Native)</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Prof. Dr. Serdar Baki Albayrak', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-05-16 03:40:16', '2022-05-16 00:40:16', '', 16, 'http://localhost/profserdar/?p=190', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(158, 1, '2022-05-04 03:46:44', '2022-05-04 00:46:44', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":31,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"about-img\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full about-img\"><img src=\"http://localhost/profserdar/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/hakkimda.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-31\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Resume</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A professor who accepts patients in the medical unit of Neurosurgery of the Brain and Nervous System (Neurosurgery). Dr. Serdar Albayrak completed his medical Dec at Marmara University Faculty of Medicine between 1991 and 1998. between 1998 and 2004, he completed his Decisional education at the Department of Neurosurgery of Istanbul University Istanbul Faculty of Medicine and earned the title of Neurosurgery Specialist (Neurosurgery).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>His research interests include treatment applications related to many diseases, especially epilepsy and brain tumors, as well as innovative applications such as brain battery surgeries (Parkinson\'s dystonia Decaying disease), tumor surgery, pain treatment, micro surgery, Gamma Knife. He also specializes in such areas as epilepsy surgery, microsurgical treatment of brain tumors, treatment of cerebral vascular tangles and bubbles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Prof. Dr. Serdar Baki Albayrak yurtdışında ABD’de Harvard Üniversitesi Hastanesi’nde ve Finlandiya’da Helsinki Üniversitesi Hastanesi’nde ameliyat ve araştırma doktoru olarak çalışmıştır.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The physician who applies surgical treatments using the most advanced methods provided by medical technology has received high-level education abroad in the USA and Germany regarding many of the procedures he has performed. In the medical field as well as our country\'s education Albayrak, many successfully completed education and work internationally, and has earned various certifications in different countries in the world having experience in 48 patients. In addition to tumor surgery, he has also conducted cancer research and has learned about innovative treatments in the field of biotechnology.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"about-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns about-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Deneyimliler</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Istanbul Marmara University Faculty of Medicine – Faculty of Medicine (Bachelor\'s Degree), 1991 – 1998</li><li>Istanbul University Istanbul Faculty of Medicine - Specialty training –Specialization in neurosurgery), 1998 – 2004</li><li>Harvard University School of Medicine - 1 Year Clinical Fellow-Scholarship Holder, 2007 – 2008</li><li>University of Helsinki - 1 Year Clinical Fellowship, 2006 – 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Experiences</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>İstanbul Marmara Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi - Tıp Fakültesi (Lisans), 1991 - 1998</li><li>İstanbul Üniversitesi İstanbul Tıp Fakültesi - Uzmanlık eğitimi -Nöroşirürji Uzmanlığı), 1998 - 2004</li><li>Harvard Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi - 1 Yıllık Klinik Burs Sahibi, 2007-2008</li><li>Helsinki Üniversitesi - 1 Yıllık Klinik Burs, 2006 - 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"about-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns about-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Awards</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Harvard University, Boston- USA, Brain Tumors, 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>BilKnown Languages</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>English</li><li>Türkçe (Native)</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Prof. Dr. Serdar Baki Albayrak', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-05-04 03:46:44', '2022-05-04 00:46:44', '', 16, 'http://localhost/profserdar/?p=158', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
