(159, 1, '2022-05-04 03:47:36', '2022-05-04 00:47:36', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":31,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"about-img\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full about-img\"><img src=\"http://localhost/profserdar/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/hakkimda.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-31\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Resume</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A professor who accepts patients in the medical unit of Neurosurgery of the Brain and Nervous System (Neurosurgery). Dr. Serdar Albayrak completed his medical Dec at Marmara University Faculty of Medicine between 1991 and 1998. between 1998 and 2004, he completed his Decisional education at the Department of Neurosurgery of Istanbul University Istanbul Faculty of Medicine and earned the title of Neurosurgery Specialist (Neurosurgery).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>His research interests include treatment applications related to many diseases, especially epilepsy and brain tumors, as well as innovative applications such as brain battery surgeries (Parkinson\'s dystonia Decaying disease), tumor surgery, pain treatment, micro surgery, Gamma Knife. He also specializes in such areas as epilepsy surgery, microsurgical treatment of brain tumors, treatment of cerebral vascular tangles and bubbles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Prof. Dr. Serdar Baki Albayrak yurtdışında ABD’de Harvard Üniversitesi Hastanesi’nde ve Finlandiya’da Helsinki Üniversitesi Hastanesi’nde ameliyat ve araştırma doktoru olarak çalışmıştır.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The physician who applies surgical treatments using the most advanced methods provided by medical technology has received high-level education abroad in the USA and Germany regarding many of the procedures he has performed. In the medical field as well as our country\'s education Albayrak, many successfully completed education and work internationally, and has earned various certifications in different countries in the world having experience in 48 patients. In addition to tumor surgery, he has also conducted cancer research and has learned about innovative treatments in the field of biotechnology.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"about-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns about-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Schools/Trainings</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Istanbul Marmara University Faculty of Medicine – Faculty of Medicine (Bachelor\'s Degree), 1991 – 1998</li><li>Istanbul University Istanbul Faculty of Medicine - Specialty training –Specialization in neurosurgery), 1998 – 2004</li><li>Harvard University School of Medicine - 1 Year Clinical Fellow-Scholarship Holder, 2007 – 2008</li><li>University of Helsinki - 1 Year Clinical Fellowship, 2006 – 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Experiences</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>İstanbul Marmara Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi - Tıp Fakültesi (Lisans), 1991 - 1998</li><li>İstanbul Üniversitesi İstanbul Tıp Fakültesi - Uzmanlık eğitimi -Nöroşirürji Uzmanlığı), 1998 - 2004</li><li>Harvard Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi - 1 Yıllık Klinik Burs Sahibi, 2007-2008</li><li>Helsinki Üniversitesi - 1 Yıllık Klinik Burs, 2006 - 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"about-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns about-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Awards</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Harvard University, Boston- USA, Brain Tumors, 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Known Languages</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>English</li><li>Türkçe (Native)</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Prof. Dr. Serdar Baki Albayrak', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-05-04 03:47:36', '2022-05-04 00:47:36', '', 16, 'http://localhost/profserdar/?p=159', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
