(187, 1, '2022-05-16 03:38:09', '2022-05-16 00:38:09', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dr. Albayrak is a dedicated academic, innovator and practising neurosurgeon who accepts and treat patients worldwide from over fifty countries so far. Hundreds of international patients were treated by his expertise in Istanbul, Turkey.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After having completed medical school and neurosurgery training in Istanbul, He did subspeciality trainings (clinical fellowships) in the top medical centers of the world- Brain tumor surgery at B&amp;W Hospital at Harvard Medical School, Boston, United States and the cerebrovascular surgery at Helsinki University Toolo Hospital, Finland.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Along with thousands of general neurosurgical cases he operated, his main interest areas include the micro-neurosurgical management of complex brain and skull base tumors, brain aneurysms, arteriovenous malformations, cavernomas, epilepsy, functional neurosurgery, and spina bifida/spasticity surgeries.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>He has numerous international publications in respected journals with hundreds of citations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Prof. Albayrak has several ongoing research projects regarding the treatment of gliomas-one of the challenging brain tumors to treat- and for restoration of neuronal transmission in spinal cord injury.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dr. Albayrak is a founding member of medical innovation group, Innoway RG and he has currently over 25 patent applications with eight granted patents.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Homepage', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-05-16 03:38:09', '2022-05-16 00:38:09', '', 12, 'http://localhost/profserdar/?p=187', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(192, 1, '2022-05-16 03:43:12', '2022-05-16 00:43:12', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":31,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"about-img\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full about-img\"><img src=\"http://localhost/profserdar/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/hakkimda.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-31\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>Professor of Neurosurgery</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dr. Albayrak is a dedicated academic, innovator and practising neurosurgeon who accepts and treat patients worldwide from over fifty countries so far. Hundreds of international patients were treated by his expertise in Istanbul, Turkey.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After having completed medical school and neurosurgery training in Istanbul, He did subspeciality trainings (clinical fellowships) in the top medical centers of the world- Brain tumor surgery at B&amp;W Hospital at Harvard Medical School, Boston, United States and the cerebrovascular surgery at Helsinki University Toolo Hospital, Finland.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Along with thousands of general neurosurgical cases he operated, his main interest areas include the micro-neurosurgical management of complex brain and skull base tumors, brain aneurysms, arteriovenous malformations, cavernomas, epilepsy, functional neurosurgery, and spina bifida/spasticity surgeries.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>He has numerous international publications in respected journals with hundreds of citations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Prof. Albayrak has several ongoing research projects regarding the treatment of gliomas-one of the challenging brain tumors to treat- and for restoration of neuronal transmission in spinal cord injury.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dr. Albayrak is a founding member of medical innovation group, Innoway RG and he has currently over 25 patent applications with eight granted patents.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"about-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns about-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Schools/Trainings</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Istanbul Marmara University Faculty of Medicine – Faculty of Medicine (Bachelor\'s Degree), 1991 – 1998</li><li>Istanbul University Istanbul Faculty of Medicine - Specialty training –Specialization in neurosurgery), 1998 – 2004</li><li>Harvard University School of Medicine - 1 Year Clinical Fellow-Scholarship Holder, 2007 – 2008</li><li>University of Helsinki - 1 Year Clinical Fellowship, 2006 – 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Experiences</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>İstanbul Marmara Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi - Tıp Fakültesi (Lisans), 1991 - 1998</li><li>İstanbul Üniversitesi İstanbul Tıp Fakültesi - Uzmanlık eğitimi -Nöroşirürji Uzmanlığı), 1998 - 2004</li><li>Harvard Üniversitesi Tıp Fakültesi - 1 Yıllık Klinik Burs Sahibi, 2007-2008</li><li>Helsinki Üniversitesi - 1 Yıllık Klinik Burs, 2006 - 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"about-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns about-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Awards</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Harvard University, Boston- USA, Brain Tumors, 2007</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Known Languages</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>English</li>